title: Loring Park Studios from $825! Open House Mon-Fri 4pm-7pm
posting_body: ['316 On The Park', '- Studios Available from $825/month (only 2 available at this price!)', 'Parking in rear.', 'Ring #104 on callbox for leasing agent.', "Amazing walkable location in Loring Park, surrounded by parks and only a few blocks away from the Sculpture Garden, Walker Art Museum, Lakes and Legends Brewing, Eggy's, Minneapolis Convention Center, Downtown is 1/2 a mile away!", '- Each unit has updated appliances, closets, and porcelain subway tile in the bathrooms.', '- ALL utilities paid by the landlord (excluding cable/internet/phone).', '- Shared On Site Laundry & Secured Bike Storage', '- NO monthly community fees!', '- Flexible move in dates with pro-rated mid-month availability', '$40 application fee', '$875-$895 Studios', '$995-$1095 1 Bedrooms', 'Security Deposit Equals One Month of Rent', '- All utilities paid by Landlord, you just pay internet/cable tv.', '- Cats allowed with a $250 non-refundable fee.', 'There are off-street parking spots via a waiting list for the above-ground $75 a month and underground $100/ month ramps.', 'Laundry is shared and on the main level.', 'Criteria to Rent:', 'Must make 3x the monthly rent in gross income to qualify.', 'Good rental history.', 'Please refer to specifics below', '- Applicant(s) must be a minimum of eighteen (18) years of age.', '- If any information herein is found to be false this application', 'will be denied and lease made with Applicant may be terminated at any time.', '- You will need a monthly income of at least 3 times the monthly rent amount.']
